General.Name: Oakridge International Ltd
General.Description: Oakridge International Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the development and distribution of nurse call hardware and software solutions for use in hospitals, aged care, disability care, and supported independent living facilities. The company was formerly known as Xped Limited and changed its name to Oakridge International Limited in April 2021. Oakridge International Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Adelaide, Australia.
